cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper involves computer vision (CV) techniques for object detection and simultaneous localization and mapping (SLAM) in robotics (RO) applications. The use of deep learning and optimization methods suggests that it may also fall under machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI) subcategories. Finally, the use of geometric constraints and camera pose estimation suggests it may also fall under graphics (GR) subcategory.
